the meaning given the term “renewable biomass” in section 211()(1) of the Clean Air Act (()(1)).oo42 U.S.C. 7545","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"8","heading":null,"label":"8","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2924/8","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2924","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2924%2F8","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “biogas” means biogas as such term is used in section 211()(1)(B)(ii)(V) of the Clean Air Act (()(1)(B)(ii)(V)).oo42 U.S.C. 7545","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
